A simple command line script to generate your API credentials to help debug issues with generating a nonce and digest.

./generate_credentials.rb my_username c26b1f244feb1744c48bf998bae5f09a

Example output

Account Name:   my_username
Nonce:          cb347820b1de3ac3eb01
Digest:         3uscAsyNwbBQs3kAA9UX8laeuxF0vhtyxIwBcqNC1XY=
Creation Time:  2010-11-20T18:11:00-0800
